prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card front. A funny and charming botanical beach scene featuring cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao (person on the left in the photo) and Jordan (person on the right). They are on a cute, stylized sandy beach with gentle turquoise waves lapping at the shore.

Instead of regular palm trees, the beach is populated with whimsical "Boba Trees" which have lush, monstera-like leaves and trunks made of oversized boba straws. Hanging from the branches are giant, ripe-looking tapioca pearls.

In the center of the scene, Lao Lao is gleefully attempting to climb one of these boba trees, reaching for a giant tapioca pearl with a huge, happy smile. Jordan stands at the base of the tree, laughing and playfully trying to catch her with outstretched arms in case she falls. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue sweatshirt and dark pants, and Jordan is wearing a tan hoodie and dark pants, consistent with the reference photo. A half-finished, oversized boba milk tea drink sits in the sand nearby.

The scene is framed by a delicate border of tropical leaves and flowers, like hibiscus and bird of paradise, in a soft watercolor style. The overall art style is clean, with bright, cheerful colors, and a whimsical storybook feel.

In the center of the composition, in a clear space above the characters, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script.
